rows.label: qst202901_0010
rows.name: Wait.

rows.label: qst202901_0020
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Hm?

rows.label: qst202901_0030
rows.name: Are you talkin' to us?

rows.label: qst202901_0040
rows.name:
I wanted to talk to
the pretty big sis...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202901_0050
rows.name: Oh, a fan of Tsuki's.

rows.label: qst202901_0060
rows.name:
[ML:Dash ]What is it, hon? Did you
need somethin' from me?

rows.label: qst202901_0070
rows.name: Um...[ML:Dash ] can I touch you?

rows.label: qst202901_0080
rows.name: Eh? [ML:Dash ]Sure, that's fine.

rows.label: qst202901_0090
rows.name: So sparkly...[ML:Dash ] It's so...[ML:Dash ] pretty.

rows.label: qst202901_0100
rows.name:
I want to wear something
like that, too...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202901_0110
rows.name: Thank you.

rows.label: qst202901_0120
rows.name:
Also, the way you talk
is so soft and pretty.

rows.label: qst202901_0130
rows.name:
It sounds more refined than
that big bro over there...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202901_0140
rows.name: Why do you keep bringin' me into this?

rows.label: qst202901_0150
rows.name:
I'm so pleased. You're
very cute yourself.

rows.label: qst202901_0160
rows.name: Hey, hey, are you a bunny big sis?

rows.label: qst202901_0170
rows.name: I'm not a bunny, I'm a Blade.

rows.label: qst202901_0180
rows.name: You're a Blade, big sis? That's so cool!

rows.label: qst202901_0190
rows.name:
My name is Tsuki. A
pleasure to meet you.

rows.label: qst202901_0200
rows.name: Tsuki?

rows.label: qst202901_0210
rows.name: That's right. Make sure you remember it.

rows.label: qst202901_0220
rows.name: Okay.

rows.label: qst202901_0230
rows.name: Hey, Tsuki-nee-chan.

rows.label: qst202901_0240
rows.name:
Why are you so sparkly
and pretty, nee-chan?

rows.label: qst202901_0250
rows.name: Why, you ask...[ML:Dash ] that's a tough one.

rows.label: qst202901_0260
rows.name: Are all Blades sparkly?

rows.label: qst202901_0270
rows.name: [ML:Dash ]No, not really.

rows.label: qst202901_0280
rows.name:
Hey, hey, where did you
learn to talk like that?

rows.label: qst202901_0290
rows.name:
It sounds more authentic than
that big bro over there...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202901_0300
rows.name:
I told you to stop
bringin' me into this.

rows.label: qst202901_0310
rows.name: I was born this way...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202901_0320
rows.name: Hey, hey, hey...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202901_0330
rows.name:
How were you born so pretty? Where
did you buy those sparkly clothes?

rows.label: qst202901_0340
rows.name: Oh, my.

rows.label: qst202901_0350
rows.name:
I can't answer so many
questions at once.

rows.label: qst202901_0360
rows.name:
She seems to have taken
quite a liking to you.

rows.label: qst202901_0370
rows.name: Good luck, Tsuki-nee-chan.

rows.label: qst202901_0380
rows.name:
Oh, you all think this is someone else's
problem. I'll remember this later...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202901_0390
rows.name:
Hey, what's your favorite
thing, nee-chan?

rows.label: qst202901_0400
rows.name: My favorite thing?

rows.label: qst202901_0410
rows.name: Yeah.

rows.label: qst202901_0420
rows.name: Let's see...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202901_0430
rows.name: I suppose I like flowers.

rows.label: qst202901_0440
rows.name: Flowers?

rows.label: qst202901_0450
rows.name:
That's right. Especially a flower called
Moondrop that only blooms at night.

rows.label: qst202901_0460
rows.name:
It's small, but it's a
beautiful white flower.

rows.label: qst202901_0470
rows.name: Hmm.

rows.label: qst202901_0480
rows.name: Hey, hey, Tsuki-nee-chan.

rows.label: qst202901_0490
rows.name:
You know, I want to be just
like you, Tsuki-nee-chan.

rows.label: qst202901_0500
rows.name: How can I do that?

rows.label: qst202901_0510
rows.name: Like me?

rows.label: qst202901_0520
rows.name: Yeah.

rows.label: qst202901_0530
rows.name: Hmm, even if you ask me that...

rows.label: qst202901_0540
rows.name:
[ML:Dash ]Right. First, you need
to play outside a lot.

rows.label: qst202901_0550
rows.name: Outside?

rows.label: qst202901_0560
rows.name:
That's right. Play a lot,
eat a lot of food...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202901_0570
rows.name:
and then, you also have to
study just a little bit.

rows.label: qst202901_0580
rows.name: Wha, study too...?[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202901_0590
rows.name: Yes, studying is important too.

rows.label: qst202901_0600
rows.name: I see... It's hard work to be pretty...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202901_0610
rows.name: So, was that helpful at all?

rows.label: qst202901_0620
rows.name: Yeah.

rows.label: qst202901_0630
rows.name:
If I try hard, can I be pretty
like you, Tsuki-nee-chan?

rows.label: qst202901_0640
rows.name:
Sure you can. You'll be a
real beauty like Tsuki.

rows.label: qst202901_0650
rows.name: Hey, Zeke.

rows.label: qst202901_0660
rows.name: I see. Thank you, Tsuki-nee-chan.

rows.label: qst202901_0670
rows.name:
The next time we meet,
I'll be pretty too.

rows.label: qst202901_0680
rows.name: Bye-bye.

rows.label: qst202901_0690
rows.name: Goodbye. Keep up the good work.

rows.label: qst202901_0700
rows.name: That girl was happy.

rows.label: qst202901_0710
rows.name:
I'm surprised. You're
good with kids, Tsuki.

rows.label: qst202901_0720
rows.name: Not at all. That was just a fluke.

rows.label: qst202901_0730
rows.name:
And you, Zeke, don't give
such careless answers.

rows.label: qst202901_0740
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Hahaha!

rows.label: qst202901_0750
rows.name:
That was payback for makin'
fun of my nice accent.

rows.label: qst202901_0760
rows.name: You really have a mean streak...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202901_0770
rows.name:
Still, I look forward to
seeing that girl again.

rows.label: qst202901_0780
rows.name: Indeed. I hope she doesn't overdo it...[ML:Dash ]
